long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Editor Logs for Bubble Apps!

One of the greatest struggles of developing on Bubble.io is not having a log of the edits you've made to your app. Perhaps a mistake was deployed live, or you are returning to a branch after some time and can't remember what you did.

Superlogs helps by tracking every edit on every branch, so you and your team can always keep a record of your app edits.
